# Rust build output (workspace-wide)
/target
**/target

# Vendored reference codebases: read-only study material (litehtml, servo,
# gumbo-parser, microtex, katex, …), cloned via git and NOT part of this repo.
# Keep our own design doc, though.
references/*
!references/ARCHITECTURE.md

# Wikipedia test corpus: bulky, local-only sample articles + per-article CSS and
# images used by hiker-htmlview's viewer/snapshot examples and wiki-article tests.
# Kept out of git deliberately — it's external content (and trips secret scanners
# on innocuous strings). Drop a copy into hiker-render/htmlview/wiki-sample/ to run
# those examples/tests; the synthetic-fixture tests run without it.
wiki-sample/

# Profiling artifacts (pprof / dhat; see the `profile` example)
flamegraph.svg
*.pb
dhat-heap.json
profile.pb

